Build a hotel management software in C and upload it on github”.


There are a lot of challenges faced by hotel managers everyday like several operational issues, handling customer’s problems, keeping a record of rooms, maintaining reputation over internet, beat the risking competition and a lot more. Here comes the use of a hotel management system to simplify the hotel operations, to burden-free and to streamline your daily task.Our team has made a cloud-based software to make your Hotel business free from a lot of work,reduce the staff needed to manage tasks such as attending phone calls ,track records which results in saving a lot of time ,minimize the manual errors and consequently decrease the overall investment which automatically increases the profits.


